sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS reencrypt
    participant OnlineSvc as feast-online Service<br/>6566/TCP (plain) or 6567/TCP (TLS)
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store Container<br/>Python/Feast SDK
    participant Backend as Backend Store<br/>(Redis/PostgreSQL/etc.)
    participant OfflineSvc as feast-offline Service<br/>8815/TCP (plain) or 8816/TCP (TLS)
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store Container<br/>Python/Feast SDK
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob<br/>ose-cli image
    participant FeastPod as Feast Deployment Pod
    participant Operator as feast-operator<br/>Go/controller-runtime
    participant RegistrySvc as feast-registry-rest Service<br/>6572/TCP (plain) or 6573/TCP (TLS)
    participant Registry as Registry Container<br/>Python/FastAPI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as ODH Notebook Pod

    Note over MLApp,Backend: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
    MLApp->>Route: gRPC request (HTTPS/443)
    Route->>OnlineSvc: reencrypt TLS
    OnlineSvc->>OnlineStore: GetOnlineFeatures<br/>Bearer JWT auth
    OnlineStore->>Backend: Read features<br/>Credentials from Secret
    Backend-->>OnlineStore: Feature values
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineSvc: gRPC response
    OnlineSvc-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>MLApp: Feature values

    Note over CronJob,Backend: Flow 2: Feature Materialization (CronJob)
    CronJob->>FeastPod: kubectl exec<br/>ServiceAccount token
    FeastPod->>Backend: Read from offline store<br/>Credentials from Secret
    Backend-->>FeastPod: Historical features
    FeastPod->>Backend: Write to online store<br/>Credentials from Secret
    Backend-->>FeastPod: Ack

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Notebook Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>(kubeflow.org/Notebook)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Notebook events
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>(feature_store.yaml)<br/>in Notebook namespace
    Notebook->>OnlineSvc: Feast SDK calls<br/>gRPC/HTTP, Bearer JWT

    Note over Operator,Registry: Flow 4: Operator Auto-Access RBAC
    Operator->>RegistrySvc: GET /api/v1/permissions<br/>HMAC-SHA256 JWT (intra-comm)
    RegistrySvc->>Registry: Forward request
    Registry-->>RegistrySvc: Permission policies
    RegistrySvc-->>Operator: JSON response
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update RBAC<br/>(ClusterRoles, Bindings)<br/>ServiceAccount token
